headline: V2X and Bell Advance to Phase II of the US Army's Flight School Next Competition
summary: V2X Inc. (NYSE: VVX) is proud to announce its advancement to Phase II of the US Army's Flight School Next (FSN) competition, as part of the Bell Textron Inc. led team alongside a remarkable network of industry teammates. This demonstrates V2X's commitment to supporting the future of Army aviation training and preparing the next generation of mission-ready pilots through cutting-edge solutions.
